properties.title: Knitting Room
properties.description: This little shop is jammed full. Yarn, yarn everywhere. They make the most of every possible nook and cranny. I like this place also because they have a lot of different kinds of knitting needles in all different sizes. Also, the people who work here are younger and hipper than in the other stores I go to.
